        ],
        "summary": "Pattern Search",
        "description": "Get all artifacts matching the given Ant path pattern. Pattern \"**\" is not supported to avoid overloading search results.\n\nNotes: Requires Artifactory Pro\n\nSince: 2.2.4\n\nSecurity: Requires a privileged user (can be anonymous)\n",
